<div class="ct-form">
    <div class="form-control">
        <h1 class="alert alert-warning">
            Sound Id : /*id*/
        </h1>
        <form method="post">
            <table>
                <tr>
                    <th>Cover (view only)</th>
                    <th>Sound File (view only)</th>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td>
                        <img src="data:image/webp;base64,"
                         width="100px" />
                         <br/>
                         <p>Cover.webp</p>
                    </td>
                    <td>
                        <audio controls src="/stream/sound//*id*/" ></audio>
                    </td>
                </tr>
            </table>
                <label>Sound Name</label>
                <input name="soundName" value="/*soundName*/" class="form-control" />
                <br/>
                <label>Description</label>
                <textarea name="soundDescription" id="edit-box">/*description*/</textarea>
                <script>
                    const editor = SUNEDITOR.create(document.getElementById("edit-box"), {
                      lang: SUNEDITOR_LANG["en"],
                      width: "100%",
                      height: "fit-content",
                      minHeight: "300px",
                      buttonList: [
                        ["undo", "redo"],
                        ["font", "fontSize", "formatBlock"],
                        [
                          "bold",
                          "underline",
                          "italic",
                          "strike",
                          "subscript",
                          "superscript",
                        ],
                        ["fontColor", "hiliteColor", "textStyle"],
                        ["removeFormat"],
                        ["outdent", "indent"],
                        ["align", "horizontalRule", "list", "lineHeight"],
                        ["save"],
                        "/",
                      ],
                    });
                    editor.onInput = () => {
                      editor.save();
                    };
                    editor.onChange = () => {
                      editor.save();
                    };
                  </script>
            <br/>
            <input onclick="editor.save();" style="text-align: right;" type="submit" class="btn btn-success"  />
        </form>
    </div>
</div>
